ontologyFramework.OFProcedureManagment.OFProcedureImplementation

Class OFJobAbstract

  • java.lang.Object
    • ontologyFramework.OFProcedureManagment.OFProcedureImplementation.OFJobAbstract
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.quartz.Job
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AlgorithmMainJob, Cleaner, ClockUpdater, ReasonerUpdater

    @PersistJobDataAfterExecution
public abstract class OFJobAbstract
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.quartz.Job
    This class encapsulate a the running method of a procedure implementing common methods. In particular it retrieve quantity that are useful during the coding of the procedure. Moreover it manage the concurrent pool size and get information about deadlines, computational time and synchronization. Please see Algorithm for more info about this entities.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Buoncomapgni Luca
